This cabinet is 3 ft. wide, 1 ft. deep, and 6 ft. high, and weighs 200 pounds. You can reduce the cabinet's size and weight by up to 95% so the cabinet fits in any pocket. Items stored inside the cabinet are shrunk or enlarged alongside it. Items removed from the cabinet immediately revert to their original size.